better in performance than angular2. needs atleast v6.10
npm: node package manager 
node -v
npm -v

npm install -g @angular/cli: -g indicates angular-cli installed globally on the system and not to be installed in every project
ng -v : if angular cli installed or not

ng new project-name: to create new project, installs packages to run angular4 application
cd project-name

ng serve: to run the application

http://localhost:4200/ to see my application


